fragment_downloaded_cb({"url":"Reference-manual_functions_both_libraries.html#both_libraries_install_vala_gir","fragment":"If set to a string value, the vala generated gir library will be\ninstalled to that path, if set to true, the default gir path will be\nused, if false the gir library will not be installed.\nIt is an error for this to be either true or a string and vala_gir to\nbe unset.\nThe default value is false.\n(since 1.11.0)\n"});